Create a program to detect the frequency of integer patterns in a given array.

### Response:
public class IntegerPatternDetection {
    public static void detectFrequency(int[] array) {
        Map<Integer, Integer> frequencies = new HashMap<>();
        for (int num : array) {
            if (frequencies.containsKey(num)) {
                frequencies.put(num, frequencies.get(num) + 1);
            } else {
                frequencies.put(num, 1);
            }
        }

        for (int num : array) {
            System.out.println("Frequency of " + num + " is: " + frequencies.get(num));
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] array = {2, 3, 4, 4, 5, 1, 2, 3, 5, 6};
        detectFrequency(array);
    }
}

